					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Josiah Hesse</h4>
												<p>Josiah Hesse, author of <em>Runner’s High</em> and the <em>Carnality</em> series, is a freelance journalist out of Denver, Colorado, covering everything from politics, science, and crime, to art, pop culture, and evangelical culture and theology. A regular contributor to <em>The Guardian</em> and <em>Vice</em>, his work has appeared in <em>Esquire</em>, <em>Newsweek</em>, <em>Men’s Health</em>, and <em>Politico</em>, among other publications.</p>
					</div>
